    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/a18dcdbf76da82fbf6db4a828ff2c388.avif?t=1734638741\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br>旧世界的女王向你发布诏令！女王陛下的领土正在扩张，需要一位精明强干的总督，带领刚刚并入版图的殖民地走向繁荣。我们将为您提供船只、殖民者和必要的工具，大片桀骜不驯的荒野等待你征服，请将它们发展成蒸蒸日上的殖民伟业，并接受女王的监督！<br><br>当然，你理应向王室奉上这些新土地所带来的收入。别忘了按时缴纳税款，并继续扩张女王陛下的殖民地。服从命令，可能会获得奖赏；如果拒绝缴税，或者胆敢宣布独立，将导致可怕的后果！<br><br>那么，总督阁下，您准备好再占一岛了吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/10877d3a672cf271a4da625ccf9be801.avif?t=1734638741\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br><br>奉女王陛下之命，即刻前往殖民帝国的边境！开疆拓土，攫取资源，为王室创造财富！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/800ee6c65e722426f109ddcab1761d7c.poster.avif?t=1734638741\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/800ee6c65e722426f109ddcab1761d7c.webm?t=1734638741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/800ee6c65e722426f109ddcab1761d7c.mp4?t=1734638741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>扬帆起航，前往新世界！插上女王陛下的旗帜，建立新殖民地，使其繁荣发展。<br></li><li>每次探索都独一无二！世界地图动态生成，结合大量手绘元素。<br></li><li>根据你的喜好进行个性化挑战！调节岛屿大小、土壤肥力、自然资源数量等等，随心所欲选择难度。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/b480f6426bdf383baec0a8f6daa07772.avif?t=1734638741\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br><br>你是总督，你做主。规划殖民地，照料好岛民，把小小前哨站变成繁华的商业大都市吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/0380374c4741553956b9e570c3ceda48.poster.avif?t=1734638741\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/0380374c4741553956b9e570c3ceda48.webm?t=1734638741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/0380374c4741553956b9e570c3ceda48.mp4?t=1734638741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>建造你喜欢的建筑：高自由度的建筑设计功能让你可以对细节进行微调，包括生产车间的布局和殖民者的行动路线，让你的殖民大业尽善尽美。<br></li><li>考虑殖民者的需求。心情愉快的殖民者会更高效、更卖力地建设你的……不对，女王陛下的殖民帝国。<br></li><li>在这片传奇的殖民地上，带领这些勤恳的殖民者打造生产线，产出必要的商品，发展社区。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/6346a3e636663bced1b45860224d6d6a.avif?t=1734638741\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br><br>再占一岛，然后……再占一岛。探索世界，建立新殖民地，再将它们相互连接，创造一个自给自足的网络——由你亲自铸就的帝国。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/c74453d48fec3c823de7a2736e6554a4.poster.avif?t=1734638741\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/c74453d48fec3c823de7a2736e6554a4.webm?t=1734638741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/c74453d48fec3c823de7a2736e6554a4.mp4?t=1734638741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>打造新舰队，探索群岛，占领岛屿，扩张版图，然后相连新领土与海外贸易路线。<br></li><li>优化生产线，增加多样性，从而创建完整的产业链，在经济上独立于旧世界。<br></li><li>不断探索，一步步将初级殖民地发展成新世界的超级大国。每个文明等级都有新的挑战、新的要求——和新的机遇。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/16d6417b8ad73b253a95093f6bf9cff5.avif?t=1734638741\" width=600 height=85 /></span><br><br>女王要求你奉上这些新土地所带来的收入。根据规定，你必须缴纳税金。但还有另一种选择——或许更合殖民者心意的选择。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/5a91f0045cf562d65923e6579959c1dc.poster.avif?t=1734638741\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/5a91f0045cf562d65923e6579959c1dc.webm?t=1734638741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1454160/extras/5a91f0045cf562d65923e6579959c1dc.mp4?t=1734638741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>维护你在王室的声誉。按时缴税，满足王室的要求，或者……<br></li><li>你是否有勇气犯下大罪？你是否有胆量违抗女王？<br></li><li>你敢不敢建立新国家，摆脱旧世界的暴政？</li></ul><br>准备好了吗？你会踏上怎样的征程？",
